Tinybackup
==========

Allows you to download backup of current database, just open direct your browser to
http://yoursite.com/tinybackups/new

Install
=======

1. install plugin
2. add config/initializers/backup.rb

TinybackupsController.class_eval do
  protected
  include AuthenticatedSystem
  include RolesRequirements  
  
  before_filter :login_required
  before_filter :require_admin
end
# or whatever it takes to authenticate user


3. add to config/routes.rb
map.resources :tinybackups

